      • enqueueReconnect

        public void enqueueReconnect(@NonNull
                             NoParameterCallback callback)
        Description copied from interface: WearableController
        Reattempt to connect to the wearable in case something stopped the previous attempt. Should not do anything if a connection is already underway (was not interrupted) or if it is already established. onSuccess() is called if the reconnection started successfully or the wearable is already connected.
        Specified by:
